Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.89,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.26,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.40,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.80,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.80,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:40.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:51.27,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:57.53,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:03.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:11.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.09,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach their next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:24.08,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat Pirates have gone to Fishman Island,\Nlocated ten thousand meters under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:29.39,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there, the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Vander Decken has been stalking the Mermaid Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The crew find themselves drawn into these events,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.93,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and things have escalated into an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.61,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, due to Hody's ruthless scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:46.04,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,an unprecedented crisis looms over Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.68,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,My axe, your target is Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.18,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah... is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.44,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.57,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.00,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,is still in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.35,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,So he finally bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:15.56,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Now Vander Decken's power will stop working,\Nand the Noah will crash down onto Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.40,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Die!  Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.55,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You fools have gotten in the way of my retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.41,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.63,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,...be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.93,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another, we have to stop the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.68,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.06,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna stop the Noah, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.31,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But you're going to have to get past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:43.23,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You can't save Fishman Island unless you defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:46.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:51.11,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,If the Noah crashes into Fishman Island,\Nthen it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:56.20,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Our kingdom and the centuries-old mission\Nto protect the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.27,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:04.68,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,That Ark, the Noah, isn't just a historical ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:16.18,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, hundreds of years past,\Nwe exchanged promises with a very important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:21.13,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,That ship has been waiting patiently\Non the ocean floor to carry out that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.73,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has not yet completed its mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:29.66,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,And now, even the techniques used to build the ship\Nhave been lost in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:34.08,Flashbacks,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Until the promised day comes,\Nwe mustn't allow the Noah to get a single scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.35,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We understand, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:41.33,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We will find out what's causing it to move\Nand deal with it appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:46.04,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save our kingdom and the Noah,\Nno matter the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:51.92,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you must be trying to think\Nof a way to stop the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:56.06,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way you could defeat me,\Neven in your own head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.62,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,So what're you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.54,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,If you just let it fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:08.69,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,then your friends will be crushed into fish food\Nwith the rest of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:13.07,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Was it just a bluff when you said that\Nyou would protect everyone, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.41,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.25,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash that boat into smithereens before it hits the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.43,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:27.36,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}if{\i0} you could do it, I already told you that the Noah holds both our past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:31.18,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Then is there another way we can save the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.43,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.57,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Decken may still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:42.52,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,If we get him to wake up, we might be able to\Nmake him change the ship's course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.92,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but what if he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.40,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry up and destroy the ship{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.03,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.04,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You two gonna start fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.84,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what's happening while you two squabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.24,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's gonna crash into Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.27,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.76,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,There are many people on the island who are precious to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.57,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Decken-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.55,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're alive, then please, aim the boat at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.64,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare the lives of everyone on Fishman island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:25.77,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the first to go to the afterlife, where you'll have a good view of Ryuuguu Kingdom's destruction.{TLC please.  I'm not sure about the use of あの世 here.  Normally that practically explicitly means "the afterlife", but I'm not entirely sure here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.61,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.16,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Manboshi dearest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.33,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Manboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.46,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.11,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.81,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.85,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,My Color of Arms is good against blunt strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.73,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,but it's useless against this kind of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,My Haki still needs training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the time to fight underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna kick his ass, we have to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.76,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want to fight on this falling ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.81,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But what you really want must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.19,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,the air on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.23,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If I get on board,\NI can take out that bastard Hody in a single hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.78,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried he might do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.47,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles will break\Nif you tear a big enough hole in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.09,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, there isn't any air on the deck anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:29.23,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,By now you must know that humans, who are helpless in situations like this, truly are inferior to fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.69,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no position to think about stopping the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.11,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.24,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.83,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I'm insulted!  You thought that you could hit {\i1}me{\i0} twice with the same attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:59.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen first?  Will Fishman Island and\Nyour friends be smashed to bits...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.96,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,or will you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:02.93,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.04,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.72,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to break my bubble again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.77,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.07,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.78,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi dearest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.82,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.66,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave Straw Hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.24,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.60,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another, I will stop Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:34.47,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nbelieve in me and do {\i1}not{\i0} go far from the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.34,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!  Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.51,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.18,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly miss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Not even if I had my eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.84,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.12,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.83,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm incredibly sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:10.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Weak-hoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.25,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi told me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Bro-hoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.41,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.59,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.67,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how many lives there are on that island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.47,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,And then{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.49,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I should be asking {\i1}you{\i0} what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.72,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that you three princes are the strongest in Ryuuguu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:35.09,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're just the foolish sons of Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:41.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,She discarded the fishman race's pride and tried to get along with humans, before dying a pathetic death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:45.22,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You're just some dumb princes who can't even protect the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Bro-hoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.16,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi dearest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.06,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you only have fake strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.09,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I couldn't stand up to you\Nmeans that I'm still inexperienced.  I'll admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.26,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.28,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,That won't hurt me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.53,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,But Hody, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.78,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to kill so many of your innocent brethren?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.62,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is your goal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.25,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What drove you to do something so terrible, Hody?!{lit. cruel}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.76,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:48.84,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi dearest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.88,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right, you dumb prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:40.02,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strength that the heavens have bestowed upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:46.44,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's time take care of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.29,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,A fake strength like that can't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.75,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,So you managed to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.38,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody, what are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:11.12,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,You say you want retribution against the humans,\Nbut you're attacking fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:16.83,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know how many of your fishmen brethren you're going to kill on Fishman Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:21.27,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,You're even going to kill\Nyour childhood friends from Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:27.17,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:40.28,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have so much hatred for humans that you've become blind with rage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:44.06,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What could have happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:47.50,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you abused by humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:52.97,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Did the humans kill\Na loved one or a dear friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:57.22,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What could have possibly happened to make you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.93,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.64,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did the humans do to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.09,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi dearest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.39,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.84,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Weak-hoshi!  Bro-hoshi's in trouble!  Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!  Hey!  Weak-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.42,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Weak-hoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:29.18,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nbelieve in me and do not go far from the Noah.{recap from previous lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.60,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!  Got it?{recap from previous lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.16,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Weak-hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.04,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.34,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Air Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.81,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one you met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.92,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We've been briefed on this terrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:53.47,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Our sensors have detected the falling Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.30,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations are proceeding according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what Bro-hoshi was talking about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.56,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you want on the deck?\NThen I'll get there first. {First part from ep 559, 21:04.86, second half was not in previous ep}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.93,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody!{idnetical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.04,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him!{Abbreviated line from 559}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.35,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,No.  Wait, Straw Hat.{identical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.65,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to wait?!{Different line from 559, but means almost the same thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.54,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have learned by now.{Identical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:17.42,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting in the water is\Ndevastatingly favorable for a fishman like Hody.{Identical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.57,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going...{identical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.43,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So what'll we do?!{identical line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.72,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan.{identical line, and last from previous episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.46,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where're you going, Bro-hoshi!{New dialogue starts with this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.38,Flashbacks,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.17,Flashbacks,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,What has happened, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:39.12,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,We may need a large amount of air soon.\NPrepare it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:39.95,Flashbacks,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.40,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.  Isn't there air on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.37,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just defeat him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:53.64,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving aside the problem of Decken,\Ndo you think Hody will just fight you on your terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:58.58,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Take this Baby Snail Phone with you,\Nin case of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.49,Flashbacks,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful in your planning.  We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.71,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama, whatever shall you do about the Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:14.25,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi said that no matter what,\Nyou and I should stick together next to the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  So Bro-hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  You there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,How're you gonna give us that air?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.36,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use all of the air in the Air Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Air Tank?  What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:31.76,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,It's an air transporting device,\Nused to deliver air to Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:36.48,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the air in the Air Tank to create a bubble,\Nit should be possible to completely enclose the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:43.92,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,But the bubble disables buoyancy,\Nso the air won't cause the Noah to float.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.30,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it won't stop the Noah's descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:53.04,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Also, to get a bubble big enough to enclose the Noah\Nwe'll have to use all the air we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.82,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,So we only get one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:20:00.51,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We have one split second when the Noah is directly beside us and if we miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.80,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be no second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:06.85,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,but basically, it's all or nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:12.91,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.  I wish we could do more,\Nbut all we can do is entrust everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.23,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We're incredibly sorry for putting you in this position{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:18.11,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me how hard it is!\NJust hurry up and give the air to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.98,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have air, I'll manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.71,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.11,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do everything in our power to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.08,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, we leave Fishman Island to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.91,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.  Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.57,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you'll accomplish by staying with the Noah's descent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.46,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the sort of idiocy I expect from a human and the Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.02,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.09,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,{Hody--This isn't even my final form!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.01,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:37.81,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, human.  Give up, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:42.00,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at you makes my skin crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.21,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I shorten my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.70,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many bystanders are hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:53.54,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I will have my revenge on you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.08,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,You absolutely can't miss.  We only get one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.43,Main,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss, Fishman Island's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.27,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat.  Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:23.15,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fukaboshi's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Bro-hoshi, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.87,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,By some miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:34.24,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:39.60,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.46,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:12.78,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People panic as the Noah approaches\Nthe island again, and they try to flee the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.14,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Strawhat Crew trust in Luffy and continue their fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:19.29,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Neptune Army finally begins its assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:23.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The fight in Gyoncord Plaza violently explodes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:26.25,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and in the middle of it all,\Na shocking truth is laid bare for all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:28.92,Main,Luffy+title1,0000,0000,0000,,A Shocking Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.52,Main,Luffy+title2,0000,0000,0000,,Hody's True Nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
